fddd235c018d1235eae31?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":842283,"node":"哔哩哔哩","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bilibili","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/dc58/e3a3/1070_mini.png?m=1645143672","description":"<p>人在国内直连 bilibili 甚至比翻墙看 YouTube 还要卡\n画质这些就不说了，为何网络还这么卡？\n今天热搜贴里说是国内运营商问题，可我怎么觉得主要是 bilibili 技术优化的问题？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842283","replies":57,"created_ts":1648004809,"created":"11:06:49","title":"为何 bilibili 体验如此之差？","author":"PatrickLe","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/PatrickLe","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/66c0/91ce/543209_mini.png?m=1622433214"},{"id":842259,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1647878519","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842259","replies":55,"created_ts":1648001751,"created":"10:15:51","title":"今天打算裸辞了，完成没有心情再敲代码，出路在哪里？","author":"mikeSbV2","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mikeSbV2","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/306e6dc2327224bc31ec5d58ba3850a0?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":842240,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1647359966","description":"刚体验了一下，真棒。就是没账号登录来做书签同步使用。<br />但是可以导入谷歌浏览器中的书签和密码，太棒了<br />真想给作者的 github 一个 start","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842240","replies":51,"created_ts":1647997047,"created":"08:57:27","title":"猫眼浏览器的 UI 真好看","author":"root01","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/root01","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7e8d/99c3/538825_mini.png?m=1640317085"},{"id":842330,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>座标在广州，工作都能准时下班，但是工资比较少。所以想搞副业。</p>\n<h2>我的设想</h2>\n<p>一定要小本经营...</p>\n<ol>\n<li>健康餐，瘦身餐。简单就是做外卖。</li>\n<li>主机游戏店</li>\n<li>私人影院</li>\n<li>乐队排练房（ band 房）</li>\n</ol>\n<p>基本租个公寓 or 写字楼就可以搞掂。查了下租金，大概每个月只要 3k~5k 。</p>\n<p>至于经营实体业的原因，是因为单纯卷技术，卷人力卷不过别人。</p>\n<p>我的计算机背景可以做些什么呢？营销方面可能有点帮助，再就是做做小程序，就想不到了。之前也没有做过生意，比较头痛。</p>\n<p>欢迎打醒...</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842330","replies":50,"created_ts":1648013808,"created":"13:36:48","title":"低工资想搞副业，不去 996 卷这样对吗...","author":"lzyfred","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lzyfred","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/eca3426aa140798254bc4a2f7093c0e0?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":842285,"node":"公司运营","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/inc","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a516/a87c/487_mini.png?m=1442496896","description":"<p>我们是小公司，请教一下有没有大佬也是刚做招投标项目不久，并且第一次中标过的，能讲讲中标经历吗？\n近期投了一些标，总是中不了标，没资源也没关系！\n万份感谢~</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842285","replies":49,"created_ts":1648004915,"created":"11:08:35","title":"有小公司刚开始做投标的吗？第一个标都是怎么中标的呀？","author":"Trinity888","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Trinity888","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6df3/fb2c/248849_mini.png?m=1642069677"},{"id":842394,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>本人前端开发，原本有一台 15 寸的 14 年款 16G macbook pro ，现在也到了要退休的年纪了，想着换个新款，现在面临做选择题：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>first</code>：M1 13 寸 16G</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>second</code>：M1 pro 14 寸 32G</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>一般来讲，14 寸的性能这么劲爆，没啥好考虑的，买就完事了；但奈何太丑，比较嫌弃;</p>\n<p>13 寸作为果厂最后一款高颜值 mac pro, 而且也是 M1 ，感觉性能应该不会太差，所以我还是比较倾向与选择 13 寸 的;</p>\n<p>纠结这两款的主要原因，就集中到了一点，内存...</p>\n<p>由于平时出现卡顿时，无法确定是因为设备老化还是内存不足，就判断不出 <code>first</code> 到底够不够日常丝滑开发所用（主要是平时没关注，想甩锅）。</p>\n<p>所以想求教一下用过 <code>first</code> 的各位前端大佬，到底丝不丝滑？</p>\n<p>也想了解一下其他开发大佬是怎么选择的呢？</p>\n<p>是选择 <code>first</code> 呢？还是放弃颜值，拥抱性能选择 <code>second</code> ?</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842394","replies":48,"created_ts":1648024909,"created":"16:41:49","title":"关于 M1 买 13 寸 还是 14 寸的选择问题...","author":"dropsio","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dropsio","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed91/71b5/426714_mini.png?m=1587987192"},{"id":842397,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1647359938","description":"<p>有个 .cc 域名，在阿里云购买，今天收到短信，提醒半个月后未完成实名认证就要停止解析。</p>\n<p>目前想迁出 aliyun ，求推荐域名托管服务商。</p>\n<p>PS：没有实名是因为买域名的时候 .cc 后缀不让实名，也不让备案。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842397","replies":47,"created_ts":1648025276,"created":"16:47:56","title":"求推荐不需要实名认证的域名托管服务商","author":"mrchi","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mrchi","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b7/4cff/323368_mini.png?m=1622346124"},{"id":842262,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842262","replies":42,"created_ts":1648002342,"created":"10:25:42","title":"宽带有 20m 的上行 也有公网 ip 能做些啥","author":"caooooooooo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/caooooooooo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b956/7e4d/500722_mini.png?m=1647998817"},{"id":842260,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>打了 N 通电话终于接到人工客服，答复说是统一集中消杀，需要 4-7 天。</p>\n<p>这效率是真的，没谁了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842260","replies":40,"created_ts":1648001777,"created":"10:16:17","title":"Studio Display 用的 ems 发货，卡在杭州萧山处理中心已经四天了。","author":"fkdog","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fkdog","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0701801586b1b3ba02b392ac42bce60e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":842282,"node":"Java","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/java","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/03af/dbd6/63_mini.png?m=1644490200","description":"今天尝试了一下 Java 9 的模块化，发现对于练手的小程序而言没有任何用处，反而限制了 IDEA 自动导包的能力。比如我尝试使用 HttpClient ，在不写 Module-Info.java 的时候能直接导入包，写了这个 info 之后，必须手动再 info 里写上要用 http 包，然后才能导入和使用。对于自己的小程序，我选择不用 module 。<br /><br />2022 年了，java 模块化已经 4 年了，大家工作中自己会主动用模块化吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842282","replies":37,"created_ts":1648004806,"created":"11:06:46","title":"CRUD 操作员们， 2022 年用上 Java9 的 Module 了吗？","author":"orangie","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/orangie","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cc9f/4a8a/505648_mini.png?m=1647682357"},{"id":842290,"node":"Visual Studio Code","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/vscode","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ede7/e2b6/867_mini.png?m=1646717416","description":"<p>我正在用的：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>darcula theme 修改默认主题,不会看起来那么刺眼</li>\n<li>git graph 查看 git 记录</li>\n<li>go/rust-analyzer/solidity 分别是 go/rust/solidity 的语言支持，挺好用</li>\n<li>markdown all in one ，也挺好用</li>\n</ul>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842290","replies":36,"created_ts":1648005702,"created":"11:21:42","title":"vscode 有哪些好用的插件？","author":"tpkeeper","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tpkeeper","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/989b587c43716484e9f57400cd9fece9?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":842375,"node":"投资","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706","description":"有 50w 闲置资金，怎么样运作能保证在风险尽量小的情况下收益最大。目标收益年利率 5%左右","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842375","replies":34,"created_ts":1648021465,"created":"15:44:25","title":"闲置资金运作问题","author":"Andydufresneguoh","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Andydufresneguoh","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1d6820b5ef794aefdfbde5f72fe6d355?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":842331,"node":"JetBrains","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/jetbrains","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2a9d/121c/912_mini.png?m=1582188474","description":"<p><img alt=\"2022-3-23 13-31-29.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D1bS8VU.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>是火星吗？\n最近使用 Goland 的最新 eap 版一直没办法自定义工具栏，我就想看看是不是配置文件没正常写出，后来发现了一个 early-access-registry.txt 文件，就在 config 目录下，我把里面的配置选项全改成 true 后，界面就完全变了，变得跟 VSCode 一样了...</p>\n<pre><code>ide.experimental.ui\ntrue\nide.experimental.ui.editor.tabs\ntrue\nide.experimental.ui.main.toolbar\ntrue\n</code></pre>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842331","replies":33,"created_ts":1648013963,"created":"13:39:23","title":"JetBrains IDE 新界面？","author":"Kisesy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Kisesy","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b44c/135c/99878_mini.png?m=1648013720"},{"id":842381,"node":"iCloud","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/icloud","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_mini.png?m=1347578950","description":"<p>最近半年被 iCloud 给折腾疯了，同步总是卡顿在正在上传和下载，一卡就是几天，平时对同步要求非常高，联系了官方多次也无法解决，想找个替代品，国内的云都有监管，目前候选是 Dropbox 、Google one ，不过得有梯子，不知道有没有用的？大家使用体验怎么样？用 Dropbox 的话，就得把 iCloud 关闭，不能同时同步到 iCloud 和 Dropbox 。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/842381","replies":32,"created_ts":1648022746,"created":"16:05:46","title":"iCloud 和 Dropbox 的选择问题","author":"wukong888","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wukong888","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a497f4884fdd6f91baf356c7d8e29806?s=24&d=retro"}]